{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6c79ad2f1f","title":"给减克家等的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b595e8f202","index":0,"year":1957,"month":1,"day":12,"articleId":"6c79ad2f1f"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji37","name":"毛泽东全集第37卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/37-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji37":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0b2d830a22","type":"title","text":"给减克家\"等的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"6c79ad2f1f"},{"id":"036ab3eb55","type":"paragraph","text":"克家同志和各位同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"6c79ad2f1f"},{"id":"b212b63d4f","type":"paragraph","text":"惠书早已收到，退复为歉！遵幅将记得起来的旧体诗词，连同你们寄来的八首，一共十八首，抄寄如另纸，请加审处。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"6c79ad2f1f"},{"id":"6392217559","type":"paragraph","text":"这些东西，我历来不愿意正式发表，因为是旧体，怕课种流传，始误青年；再则诗味不多，没有什么特色。既然你们以为可以刊载，又可为已经传抄的几首改正错字，那末，就照你们的意见","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"6c79ad2f1f"},{"id":"51cb903a61","type":"subtitle","text":"办吧。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"6c79ad2f1f"},{"id":"d054a944df","type":"paragraph","text":"《诗刊》出版，很好，祝它成长发展。诗当然应以新诗为主体，旧诗可以写一些，但是不宜在青年中提倡，因为这种体裁束缚思想，又不易学。这些话仅供你们参考。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"6c79ad2f1f"},{"id":"0342612528","type":"paragraph","text":"同志的敬礼！","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"6c79ad2f1f"},{"id":"27507d047d","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"6c79ad2f1f"},{"id":"489592c240","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五七年一月十二日","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"6c79ad2f1f"},{"id":"6c392968b7","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]减克家，当时任中国作家协会书记处书记、《诗刊》主编。","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"6c79ad2f1f"}],"page":{"id":"f974d30623","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"6c79ad2f1f","start":225,"end":225}}}},"__N_SSG":true}